    {
      "id": "battle_select_10814_1",
      "desc": "############ 蛛巢中居學徒以實瑪利 ############",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>剛才那個動作你看到沒？那個細節，天啊，簡直絕了……\n是這樣動嗎？還是——不對，應該像<i>這樣</i>？</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_endcommand_10814_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>這下絕對超帥的！</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_enemy_break_10814_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>嘿嘿。你氣炸了嗎老兄？你能拿我怎樣？</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_break_10814_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>啊啊！</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_kill_10814_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>哈！想得美，笨蛋~</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_dead_10814_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>媽……媽媽……</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_s3_10814_1_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>這是放大招的最佳角度吧？</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_s3_10814_1_2",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>接招吧！紫羅蘭~破碎猛擊！！！</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_s3_10814_1_3",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>啊！好像不是……管它的猛擊！</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_special_10814_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>看你盯的方向……我知道媽媽超帥的……</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_special_10814_2",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>雖然比不上媽媽的……但我也能邊切邊烤哦，知道嗎？</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_special_10814_3",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>怒氣值……滿了。</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_special_10814_4",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>哦？今天留在蛛巢了嗎？那……你看了我跟你說的《驟雨之刃》了嗎？啊，等、等等！別跑啊！</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_special_10814_5",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#ff9500>果然媽媽是最棒的~！</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_select_11214_1",
      "desc": "############ 提燈E.G.O格里高爾 ############",
      "dlg": "<color=#a0522d>可悲的是，住在我森林裡的只有死者。如今，我唯一能做的……就是殺死那頭野獸。</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_endcommand_11214_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#a0522d>提升E.G.O同調中……</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_enemy_break_11214_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#a0522d>別動。</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_break_11214_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#a0522d>唔……</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_kill_11214_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#a0522d>我是來拯救你的。</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_dead_11214_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#a0522d>原來……就這樣結束了嗎……</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_s3_11214_1_5",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#a0522d>照亮前方的路吧，這樣我才能看清那些必須拯救的生命。</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_s3_11214_1_6",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#a0522d>我現在看清了……我必須拯救的人是誰！</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_special_11214_1",
      "desc": "",
      "dlg": "<color=#a0522d>到這邊來……我一定會確保你的安全。</color>"
    },
    {
      "id": "battle_select_11015_1",
